開放示範單位。<br />\n<br />\n市場消息指，首日截至晚上6時半左右, 御海灣首日已錄得超過500入票，以首批推出88伙單位，超額近4.7倍。為配合抗疫措施，示範單位將採取透過指定地產代理預約形式供公眾參觀。"},{"pid":"2e69cc270fd59a07f4f8a115fc1b349fc6c7377d","tid":2113712,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:14:22.000Z","msg":"正常嘅<br />\n咁嘅時候應該都隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n唔使見客都可以入票"},{"pid":"53f2e63929a501319e8d3d441bfd042854aa0125","tid":2113712,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"打稅用未折價？"},{"pid":"59c06c1e87b0711c81e7a88efe33a0596c373eb4","tid":2113712,"uid":75355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2e69cc270fd59a07f4f8a115fc1b349fc6c7377d","tid":2113712,"uid":341649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:14:22.000Z","msg":"正常嘅<br />\n咁嘅時候應該都隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n唔使見客都可以入票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T14:11:03.000Z","msg":"ICC幾時先可以有確診？好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed31933e5979fc50ea6be029d5daef16f4250dae","tid":2113712,"uid":64648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53f2e63929a501319e8d3d441bfd042854aa0125","tid":2113712,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"打稅用未折價？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T15:37:26.000Z","msg":"用最後折完價"},{"pid":"cbd12562584bb8b99e092bb0f8b4b7f958fb42ff","tid":2113712,"uid":75355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:02:37.000Z","msg":"又加推50伙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c78d74e042ca6e7fdcdbbf07344c3b47e8c29af","tid":2113712,"uid":244758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"50人但有一千飛喎"},{"pid":"c3594550c5efa91bf511c0e2c174b8c123d9defa","tid":2113712,"uid":75355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c78d74e042ca6e7fdcdbbf07344c3b47e8c29af","tid":2113712,"uid":244758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T12:27:4